<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">4月7日，江西省副省长孙洪山莅临江西软件职业技术大学，调研了区块链专家小村、元宇宙实验室、区块链学院、北斗通航创新应用研究中心 、退役军人教育学院，以及学生公寓和食堂等。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">省政府副秘书长杜章彪，省委教育工委委员、省教育厅总督学曹伴好，南昌市湾里管理局党工委书记龚志强，先锋软件集团董事局主席、学校创始人陈苏，学校理事长陈方平，校党委书记、督导专员江延湖，执行校长范红铭等领导陪同调研。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2010%3A00%3A29B22.jpg?Expires=2027901630&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=fPGmt84nE4f1Kgm9gcAIfXGkbws%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 433px;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">陈苏介绍了先锋软件三十年和学校二十年的发展历程、特色、理念，以及学校“升本改大”后的职业本科办学情况等。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">先锋软件和学校自2015年开始探索区块链基础和应用研究、人才培养、产业推进等，先后推动成立江西省区块链行业协会、江西省区块链学会、江西省区块链专家委员会、区块链行业协会和大数据与区块链联盟专业委员会等；元宇宙实验室囊括了元宇宙原生、元宇宙共生、元宇宙相生、元宇宙孪生、区块链、AI人工智能、数字虚拟人等核心技术，为社会打通从教、学、研、创到元宇宙产业的整体脉络；区块链学院自2019年6月成立以来，致力于区块链技术的人才培养与应用研究，成功实施了江西省政法委基于区块链电子卷宗传输项目，开发了基于区块链技术的智慧党建项目，探索了“区块链+教育”应用场景，完成了省教育区块链首批15个骨干节点高校联盟链的开发工作，还通过“区块链+农业”项目，让江西井冈蜜柚“上链”提价。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2010%3A06%3A44%E5%AD%9034.jpg?Expires=2027902004&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=5xq6KCqu450ChDRW4PL4OIpOpP0%3D" alt="" width="650" height="463" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 463px;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2010%3A10%3A37%E5%8F%8824.jpg?Expires=2027902237&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ZEsqhIcVT2L4LyCmJGeTeBkMi6Q%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 433px;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">北斗通航创新应用研究中心以建设全国一流北斗+无人机军民两用创新应用研发基地为目标、聚焦低空无人机管控、反无人机、北斗导航综合应用等领域，围绕无人机组网遥感、“北斗+”融合应用等关键性技术研究，打造一个具有综合性、应用性和开放性的多学科交叉创新平台；退役军人教育学院是江西省首家共建退役军人教育学院，是江西省退役军人职业技能培训定点承训单位、江西省首批退役军人就业创业园地等，该学院构建了以退役军人学历教育提升、职业技能培训、就业服务指导、创新创业孵化四大板块为重点的退役军人教育服务体系。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2009%3A44%3A34A4.png?Expires=2027900675&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=hgT75oOdwJNW8V1Ob6OfHi6%2B9IQ%3D" alt="" width="650" height="496" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 496px;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2010%3A16%3A11643.jpg?Expires=2027902571&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Zokc%2FPism4vnXSspy2PsKe83B0c%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 433px;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">在调研平安校园建设中，孙洪山走进学生公寓，听取了学生公寓自我管理情况介绍，对一站式学生社区服务中心的做法予以肯定，并与辅导员、楼长、学生等亲切交流；在学生第一食堂，孙洪山驻足看菜品菜价、AI智慧自选餐厅以及仔细听食堂管理介绍等。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2010%3A27%3A15888.jpg?Expires=2027903235&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=qIwWrKonnxlH79cj4tLC8vVYr20%3D" alt="" width="650" height="439" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 439px;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2010%3A21%3A16378.jpg?Expires=2027902877&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=MK4QPfn%2FH0trOcduQaVkk4Ef024%3D" alt="" width="650" height="495" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 495px;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">孙洪山肯定了学校的办学理念、办学特色、办学成果等，赞赏了校园生态环境优美。他强调，要认真贯彻落实习近平总书记关于建设教育强国的重要论述和考察江西重要讲话精神，聚焦“走在前、勇争先、善作为”的目标要求，全面贯彻党的教育方针，落实立德树人根本任务，为党育人、为国育才；始终坚持高等职业教育的属性和特色，推动学校高质量内涵式发展取得更大成效；要紧扣国家战略需求和地方发展需要，主动担当作为，聚焦和围绕数字经济发展，落实江西省制造业重点产业链现代化建设“1269”行动计划，为国家培养又红又专的数字经济人才作贡献；要始终守牢校园安全底线，增强学生安全防范意识，严防严管严控校园食品安全风险，全力保障师生身体健康和生命安全。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p>